title: Airport Spotting: Alia Bhatt, Hrithik Roshan & Ranveer Singh Clicked By Shutterbugs
text: Several celebrities were spotted at the airport last night. Actress Alia Bhatt set new trends for airport fashion and made us fall in love with her Star Wars tee. Also, Kaabil star Hrithik Roshan who is currently busy promoting his film as spotted at the airport. Ranveer Singh who is busy shooting for Padmavati was also seen there.
